{"tid":2063681,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"係我唔欣賞定廣東麻雀真係咁悶？","createTime":"2020-06-14T08:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T00:33:14.000Z","uid":64994,"like":19,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"7c759cd577bfc3489bd3fa165b89e07aace048bc","tid":2063681,"uid":64994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:12:05.000Z","msg":"只從學識玩日本牌之後就更加覺得廣東牌悶<br />\n特別係玩三番起糊<br />\n係有時副牌得意啲可以諗玩其他花臣嘢<br />\n但基本上一開牌就淨係可以諗做混一色定對對糊<br />\n<br />\n之後碰隻上隻就全枱都知你做咩<br />\n已經無得再靠其他人打嘢俾你<br />\n淨低嘅就得等運到  希望可以摸到返嚟<br />\n<br />\n而且因為大部份人都做混一色<br />\n成日都會同其他人做同一隻花色<br />\n如果轉唔切  果場已經收得皮唔駛食糊<br />\n<br />\n所以我完全唔明啲人係點打通宵麻雀<br />\n係我漏咗啲嘢唔識欣賞定廣東牌真係咁悶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bee8c0d28f6ad59cd5ba27eb111479443d264ea","tid":2063681,"uid":57844,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:13:51.000Z","msg":"真正廣東牌好多花款，好常轉章變陣<br />\n係香港化後少左好多"},{"pid":"f0d44d85f377df5600e680365eb8a3c253ce50af","tid":2063681,"uid":69125,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:14:35.000Z","msg":"咁你可以8番起糊咪迫全世界造牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5e97f50d0fd8c64f1f72edd80312fd7f83be7b","tid":2063681,"uid":3358,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f0d44d85f377df5600e680365eb8a3c253ce50af","tid":2063681,"uid":69125,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:14:35.000Z","msg":"咁你可以8番起糊咪迫全世界造牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:17:49.000Z","msg":"就係你D人<br />\n講緊本身個rule悶<br />\n你就叫人8番起糊<br />\n個問題根本冇解決過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你玩8番就唔知人地做咩牌咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩過日麻都知人地玩法好玩好多"},{"pid":"b6ac01bd9542e048f76450660cd69ccab4f00312","tid":2063681,"uid":77461,"like":21,"dislike":8,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:18:16.000Z","msg":"只係你接觸到新嘢之後 覺得自己懶係識嘢 與別不同<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb0dce3a0496a3d31b3cc40d5540d3b8fbc27b2","tid":2063681,"uid":16528,"like":14,"dislike":44,"score":-30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:26:59.000Z","msg":"唔關廣東牌、中國牌定日本牌事<br />\n麻雀根本就係悶，又悶又嘈 <br />\n基本上識玩少少既人<br />\n都知另外三家做緊咩章，等緊咩牌<br />\n自己無機會時攬撚住啲牌一齊死<br />\n無聊至極<br />\n<br />\nPoker就唔同<br />\n玩法千變萬化<br />\n心理戰 數學 賭博 紀律集於一身<br />\n有牌都唔一定贏<br />\n無牌可以bluff走full house<br />\nPoker枱上充滿任何可能性<br />\n<br />\n仲有麻雀最撚on9係自摸要位位比錢<br />\n我打poker唔想輸錢咪唔入池<br />\n輸贏基本上都係自己控制<br />\n麻雀一晚bad run真係玩撚完<br />\n<br />\n東方人玩麻雀<br />\n鬼佬玩poker<br />\n所以係鬼佬稱霸世界<br />\n要自強 就今日開始棄麻雀 打poker啦"},{"pid":"ec3fcdddb355e69dcbb15d453da5e97aff02235c","tid":2063681,"uid":246986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:27:21.000Z","msg":"想快咪打返雞平糊 跑馬仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打正宗台灣牌都可以好快"},{"pid":"9db5104f0dcaaf6a8c94615d2f92f9d056d9301e","tid":2063681,"uid":126226,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"ec3fcdddb355e69dcbb15d453da5e97aff02235c","tid":2063681,"uid":246986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:27:21.000Z","msg":"想快咪打返雞平糊 跑馬仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打正宗台灣牌都可以好快"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:30:28.000Z","msg":"跑馬仔開心好多...快上快落<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9594ec3f7b470e245756c23e191987939f0318e","tid":2063681,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c5e97f50d0fd8c64f1f72edd80312fd7f83be7b","tid":2063681,"uid":3358,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":